She was all alone.[p]
But I have Cheryl.[p]
The girl in the picture is appealing to me for something.[p]
In the painful silence I can feel a spiritual message.[p]
After wavering, I removed the picture from the frame and slid it into my pocket.[p]
And then I left the room.[p]


